# Keuwo Backend - Quick Index

Real-estate rent/buy platform. NestJS 11 + TypeScript, Drizzle ORM (PostgreSQL), BullMQ (Redis), EventEmitter2 internal bus, Socket.io (planned migration to AWS AppSync), Resend email, JWT auth with 2FA.

## Module map (`src/modules/`)

| Module | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `auth` | Login/JWT, sessions with deviceId, 2FA challenges, email/phone confirmation |
| `properties` | Property CRUD, lifecycle draft→published→archived, availability, visits |
| `listings` | Listing CRUD, lifecycle draft→published→paused→closed, dealType, interaction tracking |
| `search` | Paginated listing search (FTS + geo + filters), search history |
| `analytics` | Behavior events consumer, user insights aggregation (`/analytics/users/:id/insights`) |
| `notifications` | Email/SMS templates and dispatch (Resend) |
| `users`, `chat`, `applications`, `contracts`, `documents`, `payments`, `visits` | Supporting domains (some are stubs) |

## Key infrastructure (`src/infrastructure/`)

- `database/drizzle/` — DrizzleService, schemas (`auth`, `real-estate`, `analytics`, `outbox`)
- `messaging/outbox/` — OutboxRepository (transactional outbox)
- `queue/` — BullMQ module + `QueueSchedulers` (repeatable jobs: `outbox-relay` 5s, `analytics` 60s)

## Core conventions

- Transactional outbox: repository writes accept an `eventsFactory(row) => DomainEvent[]` callback and persist domain rows + outbox events in one Drizzle transaction. Build events with `buildDomainEvent()` (`src/shared/domain/events/`).
- Event topics live in `src/events/contracts/integration-events/keuwo-events.examples.ts` (`EVENT_TOPICS`).
- Domain enums: `PROPERTY_AMENITIES` + availabilities in `src/modules/properties/domain/property.constants.ts`; `LISTING_DEAL_TYPES` in `src/modules/listings/domain/listing.constants.ts`.
- Pagination: use `buildPaginatedResult()` / `PaginatedResult<T>` from `src/shared/application/pagination/pagination.ts`. Never return unbounded lists.
- Drizzle `numeric` columns map to strings: convert with `String(value)` on write, `Number(value)` on read.
- Global `ValidationPipe` (transform + whitelist + implicit conversion). DTOs use class-validator; conditional requirements use `@ValidateIf`.
- Path aliases: `@app`, `@modules`, `@infrastructure`, `@shared`, `@auth`, `@config`, `@events`, `@jobs` (see tsconfig paths).

## Commands

- Tests: `npm test` (jest, `*.spec.ts` in `test/unit` and `test/integration`)
- Typecheck src only: `npx tsc -p tsconfig.build.json --noEmit`; with tests: `npx tsc --noEmit`
- Lint: `npm run lint` / `npm run lint:fix` (prettier formatting is enforced; run lint:fix after edits)
- Migrations are hand-written SQL in `drizzle/migrations/NNNN_name.sql` (latest: 0012)

